	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe nester? It's not the most accurate emulator, but it's very easily modified to support the mapper you are using if it doesn't already. I have my own modified version which supports our custom mappers.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nester.sourceforge.net/license.html">http://nester.sourceforge.net/license.html</a><!-- m -->

		

		</td>
